\loch\af2\dbch\af2\hich\f2\strike0\ul\cf2 Raymond Moley}{\rtlch\af2\alang1025\afs24\ltrch\b0\i0\fs20\lang1033\langnp1033\langfe1033\langfenp1033\loch\af2\dbch\af2\hich\f2\strike0\ulnone\cf2  was one of US President Franklin Roosevelt's most heeded advisers, who coined the term "New Deal".}
{\rtlch\afs24\ltrch\fs24\par}\pard\plain\itap0\s0\fi0\sb200\sa0\aspalpha\aspnum\adjustright\ltrpar\li0\lin0\ri0\rin0\qj\faauto\sl260\slmult0\rtlch\afs24\ltrch\fs24{\rtlch\af2\alang1025\afs24\ltrch\b0\i0\fs20\lang1033\langnp1033\langfe1033\langfenp1033
